				<div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
												<div class="tab-pane slide-down" id="nav-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-1" tabindex="0">
								<div class="tab-data mt-6 mt-sm-8 d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-8 align-items-sm-end align-items-start justify-content-between">
									<div>
										<p class="s1 s2-lg s3-sm tab-title">Racket Sports</p>
										<p class="b2 b3-lg b4-sm tab-desc mt-3 mt-sm-4">Rally your way to fitness at VEO Fitness Centers with our exhilarating racket sports experiences. From intense tennis matches to fast-paced squash games, our top-notch facilities ensure an unmatched thrill on the court, propelling you towards your fitness goals with every swing and serve.</p>
									</div>
																			<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.veofitness.com/en/movements/racket-sports/" >
											View details										</a>
																	</div>
								<div class="tab-media mt-8 mt-sm-9">
																			<img width="1152" height="496" decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201152%20496'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Racket Sports" data-lazy-src="https://veofitness.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/RACKETS-AT-VEO.jpg"><noscript><img width="1152" height="496" decoding="async" src="https://veofitness.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/RACKETS-AT-VEO.jpg" alt="Racket Sports"></noscript>
																	</div>
							</div>
												<div class="tab-pane slide-down" id="nav-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-2" tabindex="0">
								<div class="tab-data mt-6 mt-sm-8 d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-8 align-items-sm-end align-items-start justify-content-between">
									<div>
										<p class="s1 s2-lg s3-sm tab-title">Strength</p>
										<p class="b2 b3-lg b4-sm tab-desc mt-3 mt-sm-4">Experience unparalleled strength training at our fitness centres. Our dynamic workouts blend cardio, mobility, and conditioning to unleash your full potential, sculpting lean muscle, boosting endurance, and empowering you to conquer every challenge with confidence and finesse.</p>
									</div>
																			<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.veofitness.com/en/movements/strength/" >
											View details										</a>
																	</div>
								<div class="tab-media mt-8 mt-sm-9">
																			<img width="1440" height="620" decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201440%20620'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Strength" data-lazy-src="https://veofitness.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/STRENGTH-AT-VEO.jpg"><noscript><img width="1440" height="620" decoding="async" src="https://veofitness.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/STRENGTH-AT-VEO.jpg" alt="Strength"></noscript>
																	</div>
							</div>
												<div class="tab-pane slide-down" id="nav-3" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-3" tabindex="0">
								<div class="tab-data mt-6 mt-sm-8 d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-8 align-items-sm-end align-items-start justify-content-between">
									<div>
										<p class="s1 s2-lg s3-sm tab-title">Gym</p>
										<p class="b2 b3-lg b4-sm tab-desc mt-3 mt-sm-4">Achieve your ideal physique at VEO Fitness Centres through our specialised bodybuilding classes, prioritising muscle development and sculpting. Under the expert guidance of our trainers, you&#8217;ll receive personalised instruction to maximise your results and unlock your full potential.</p>
									</div>
																			<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.veofitness.com/en/movements/gym/" >
											View details										</a>
																	</div>
								<div class="tab-media mt-8 mt-sm-9">
																			<img width="1152" height="496" decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201152%20496'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Gym" data-lazy-src="https://veofitness.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/GYM-AT-VEO.jpg"><noscript><img width="1152" height="496" decoding="async" src="https://veofitness.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/GYM-AT-VEO.jpg" alt="Gym"></noscript>
																	</div>
							</div>
												<div class="tab-pane slide-down" id="nav-4" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-tab-4" tabindex="0">
								<div class="tab-data mt-6 mt-sm-8 d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-8 align-items-sm-end align-items-start justify-content-between">
									<div>
										<p class="s1 s2-lg s3-sm tab-title">Martial Arts</p>
										<p class="b2 b3-lg b4-sm tab-desc mt-3 mt-sm-4">Transform your fitness journey with specialized martial arts training and unlock a new level of strength, agility, and self-discipline. Experience improved cardiovascular health, enhanced flexibility, and heightened mental focus as you hone your skills with our certified trainers.</p>
									</div>
																			<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.veofitness.com/en/movements/martial-arts/" >
